A classic ginger shop with tea leaves hand-picked from Darjeeling, India which lies in North-eastern part of IndiaHow to use -


You can check status of my last order by saying "status of my order" or "start quiz" to start quiz campaign if any.

Note: This skill takes your email id to do all the functionality. Incase you have not created account with us, please visit https://ginger-tea-store.myshopify.com and create an order to use the skill properly.
